upload
******


Description
===========

Upload is a container that can be used to put all the relevant and
related on-demand upload based log files together.


Available Commands
==================

* delete

* delete-upload-file

* delete-upload-warning

* get

* get-unprocessed-bucket

* list

* list-upload-files

* list-upload-warnings

* set-unprocessed-bucket

* upload-log-events-file

* upload-log-file

* validate-file

* validate-source-mapping
